snippet.title: Wizard of Legend 2 - Humble Games Showcase 2025 Trailer
snippet.description: Face perilous magical trials in the fast-paced rogue-lite follow-up to the acclaimed original, featuring co-op and vibrant new 3D visuals. Master new Arcana and elements, experiment with spell combinations, and become the next Wizard of Legend!
